Uvarus pictipes
(Lea, 1899): 
Watts (1978
: 33, comb. nov., redescription); 
Watts (1985
: 24, checklist); 
Lawrence et al. (1987
: 335, catalogue); 

Bistroem
(1988

: 10, systematics); 
Hendrich (2001a
